{"tid":909234,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"黃埔花園呎價劈落1.2萬 平過新界樓","createTime":"2018-11-20T08:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T09:54:59.000Z","uid":60281,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"3ee6e361bba7cbb003c797e196fa6ce3188de483","tid":909234,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n市區藍籌屋苑連環冧價。消息指紅磡黃埔花園1期3座中層A室，實用面積777方呎，4房間隔，今年9月放盤，原叫價1,180萬元，近日累劈180萬至1,000萬元終易手，呎價僅12,870元，低市價最少15%，呎價平過新界不少上車屋苑。單位屬收租物業，有租客居住中，買家不能睇樓。<br />\n<br />\n賣方1990年以147.5萬元買入單位，止賺852.5萬元離場。<br />\n<br />\n今年9月至10月樓市最癲時期，1期錄得四宗造價逾1,200萬元的同類四房成交，其中1期1座高層C室，9月以1,300萬元成交，呎價16,731元，是次成交較之低23%。<br />\n<br />\n黃埔花園交投淡靜，本月暫錄約3宗成交。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181120/58936317\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181120%2F58936317&d=Q2fpNZjU8e7BPMXOjrwcQdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=7bc423ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181120%2F58936317&h=899ad979\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181120/58936317</a>"},{"pid":"d812a54a49a347be6e7031290bfbe58f5bf735da","tid":909234,"uid":188635,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"連租約正常呀"},{"pid":"5e718670b132e989b5392a431e71ce714e7a7a4b","tid":909234,"uid":87218,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:38:41.000Z","msg":"連租約，入面可能爛曬，唔計啦"},{"pid":"76f8ff3bb0c92fb58bf802633830e3d2862b8ed6","tid":909234,"uid":62822,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:40:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"182eeb9eb1